Package org.bson.codecs.pojo.annotations

Annotation Type BsonIgnore


  • @Documented
@Target({METHOD,FIELD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface BsonIgnore
    An annotation that configures a property to be ignored when reading and writing to BSON

    Note: Requires the Conventions.ANNOTATION_CONVENTION

    Since:
    3.5
    See Also:
    Conventions.ANNOTATION_CONVENTION
